<body>
    <h1>Mesh Developer Tools</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><br></p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation"><span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluen=
ce-information-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>The Mesh Developer Tools are a set of command-line tools designed to pro=
vide a set of basic capabilities to enable development of Components (APIs,=
 Proxies, Listeners, etc.) to run in the Mesh Platform.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<p class=3D"title conf-macro-render">On-boarding to Artifactory, Bitbucket =
&amp; Bamboo</p><span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning=
 confluence-information-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>This page assumes you are already registered as a user of Artifactory, B=
itbucket &amp; Bamboo. If this is not the case, please read the guide at <a=
 href=3D"/display/MESH/Developer+Prerequisites">Developer Prerequisites</a>=
 before you proceed to the steps below.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><style type=3D"text/css">/*<![CDATA[*/
