></li>
<li><a href=3D"#MeshDeveloperTools-MavenChecklist">Maven Checklist</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<p></p>
<h2 id=3D"MeshDeveloperTools-InitialSetup">Initial Setup</h2>
<p>Once you are registered as a user of Artifactory and Bitbucket, run the =
following command on Windows command prompt or powershell</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">powershe=
ll.exe -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command "iex ((New-Object System=
.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projec=
ts/WDP2/repos/mesh-developer-wsl/raw/Get-Tokens.ps1'))"</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>For Mac, you need to run the following</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bash -c =
"$(curl -fsSL https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDP2/repos/mesh=
-developer-wsl/raw/get-tokens.sh)"</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>These scripts will create required environment variables for your user p=
rofile such as ARTIFACTORY_ACCESS_TOKEN, BITBUCKET_ACCESS_TOKEN, PIP_INDEX_=
URL, NPM_CONFIG_REGISTRY etc</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e"><span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-i=
nformation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>The above scripts need to be rerun, when ARTIFACTORY_ACCESS_TOKEN and BI=
TBUCKET_ACCESS_TOKEN expire- to refresh the local environment variables.</p=
>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"MeshDeveloperTools-prerequisitesPre-requisiteTools"><span class=
=3D"confluence-anchor-link" id=3D"MeshDeveloperTools-prerequisites"></span>=
Pre-requisite Tools</h2>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation"><span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluen=
ce-information-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>For Mac setup we suggest brew instead of choco, see the page&nbsp;<a hre=
f=3D"/display/MESH/Homebrew">Homebrew</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
